  ## 11. Rollout and Migration Plan

  • Proposed: Phased Approach:
    • Phase 1: Add optional  telemetry  Cargo feature, introduce the
    client/src/telemetry.rs  module, and configure the ZST metrics interface.
    • Phase 2: Instrument tracing spans using  tracing  macros across the KV
    operations in  lib.rs  and  shard.rs .
    • Phase 3: Instrument metrics recorders inside the write batch and read
    batch streams. Expose the  meter_provider  setter on  Config  when the
    telemetry  feature flag is active.
    • Phase 4: Instrument background loops (heartbeat and assignment task).


