    •  db.system :  "oxia"
    •  db.name : Namespace name
    •  db.operation :  "put"
    •  db.oxia.shard_id : Targeted shard ID
    •  error.type : Set on failure.
  • Error / Status Behavior: Fails with  Error  status on version mismatches
